<paragraph id="IFRS03_44" base="F4230538" principles="no"><paranum>44</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 3"/><data name="paranum" value="44"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS03_P0176">In a <xref base="F4230842" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0304">business combination<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0025"/></ph></xref> achieved by contract alone, the <xref base="F4230833" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0297">acquirer<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0005"/></ph></xref> shall attribute to the <xref base="F4230879" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0325">owners<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0281"/></ph></xref> of the <xref base="F4230829" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0296">acquiree<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0004"/></ph></xref> the amount of the acquiree&#x2019;s net assets recognised in accordance with this IFRS. In other words, the <xref base="F4230851" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0308">equity interests<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0104"/></ph></xref> in the acquiree held by parties other than the acquirer are a <xref base="F4230876" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0323">non&#x2011;controlling interest<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0260"/></ph></xref> in the acquirer&#x2019;s post&#x2011;combination financial statements even if the result is that all of the equity interests in the acquiree are attributed to the non&#x2011;controlling interest.</p></body></paragraph>